summary: This is my CME save of my Dragonborn.
descriptionHtml:
I have created a guide [url=http://lowegulefigure.com/how-to-create-cute-character-on-skyrim/]here [/url]about how to make create cute character. I will share my CME_save character preset to Nexus so that it'd useful for you who need it. Just don't use it for follower mod you created unless you ask me first. I don't use ENB since my PC is a low end PC, so the screenshot I provided won't be as good as other. 

To use it correctly please follow the guide and install the recommended mods.
